content.Thu.000: This place is full of memories for me. Thank you so much for restoring it.$h
content.2.001: Oh dear, is it an emergency? Why are you here?$s
content.winter_17.000: This is one of the newer traditions in Pelican Town... but we've taken to it rather quickly. Haven't we, George?
content.23.000: Now now, dear... It's important that Doctor Harvey takes a good look at you. He's a nice young man! Behave yourself, for your dear old wife's sake.
content.23.001: Could you check his lungs? He's been wheezing lately.
content.2.000: When you get to be my age you have to see the doctor more often.
